      "comment": "CANTIAMO (1) is back after a four-month spell. Tested twice at Group 3 level last prep, the pick of the runs a first-up sixth to the talented Point Barrow down the Flemington straight in Cup week. Cruised home to win a recent Scone trial. Class runner who looks forward enough to take care of this field. PRECIOUS GIRL (3) returned from a brief spell with a comfortable all-the-way win in a 900m Newcastle maiden a fortnight ago. Back better than ever and will give them something to catch. Veteran mare KEV'S GIRL (6) maintains a zest for racing with a couple of strong recent results. Six-time winner at this trip so cannot be left out of calculations. CAPITAL DANCER (4) fitter fourth-up and is best of the rest.",
